issue.title: Clear terminal before displaying a new post.
issue.body:
**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**
I hate when my terminal window gets filled up with output. It makes the posts hard to read.

**Describe the solution you'd like**
I'd like the previous output cleared before continuing to the next post.

**Describe alternatives you've considered**
N/A

**Additional context**
N/A

issue.title: Greatly improve extensibility.
issue.body:
**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**
autostack is very tightly coupled to python. However, the goal is to make it so that it can be extended to be used with any language.

**Describe the solution you'd like**
Use this repository as the autostack "core," decoupled from python.

**Describe alternatives you've considered**
N/A

**Additional context**
N/A

issue.title: Clean up the user interface.
issue.body:
**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**
The user interface is not very appealing/pleasing to the eye.

**Describe the solution you'd like**
Use something like [Inquirer.js](https://github.com/SBoudrias/Inquirer.js) to "beautify" the user interface.

**Describe alternatives you've considered**
N/A

**Additional context**
N/A

issue.title: Custom Queries
issue.body:
**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**
I don't like how you can't provide custom Stack Overflow queries, only (Y/n).

**Describe the solution you'd like**
I'd like the ability to create custom Stack Overflow queries, in addition to answering (Y/n) after a post is displayed.

**Describe alternatives you've considered**
N/A

**Additional context**
N/A
